he handicapped, who lived in Germany and countries annexed by the Nazis. An enormous list of countries including <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/hungary\/\" target=\"_blank\">Hungary<\/a>, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/poland\/\" target=\"_blank\">Poland<\/a>, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/netherlands\/\" target=\"_blank\">The Netherlands<\/a>, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/\" target=\"_blank\">France<\/a>, <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/\" target=\"_blank\">Italy<\/a>, and so on! (<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\" href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Areas_annexed_by_Nazi_Germany#\/media\/File:World_War_II_in_Europe,_1942.svg\" target=\"_blank\">See list<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105718\/victims-Auschwitz-Birkenau.jpg\" alt=\"victims Auschwitz Birkenau\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"victims Auschwitz Birkenau\" class=\"wp-image-46773 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105718\/victims-Auschwitz-Birkenau.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105718\/victims-Auschwitz-Birkenau-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105718\/victims-Auschwitz-Birkenau-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105718\/victims-Auschwitz-Birkenau-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105718\/victims-Auschwitz-Birkenau-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com