d into a cattle car, with just one toilet, and no food or water; terrible when you consider that the length of the train journeys were between 4 to 10 days!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Auschwitz tour:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/auschwitz-tickets\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book it here online.<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105749\/visit-Auschwitz-krakow-poland.jpg\" alt=\"visit Auschwitz krakow poland\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"visit Auschwitz krakow poland\" class=\"wp-image-46760 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105749\/visit-Auschwitz-krakow-poland.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105749\/visit-Auschwitz-krakow-poland-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105749\/visit-Auschwitz-krakow-poland-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105749\/visit-Auschwitz-krakow-poland-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105749\/visit-Auschwitz-krakow-poland-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105749\/visit-Auschwitz-krakow-pola