ople into groups. Those considered unfit for work, including young children, pregnant women, and the elderly, were ordered to take showers. Unfortunately, these showers were actually gas chambers. Afterwards, their bodies were burned in crematory ovens.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>&#x201C;75% of each transport to Auschwitz were killed when arriving and showering.&#x201D;<\/p><\/blockquote>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/45230&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105705\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-guide.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105705\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-guide-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105705\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-guide-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"How to visit Auschwitz Concentration Camp in Poland\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-why-auschwitz\">Why Auschwitz?&#xA0;<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Auschwitz had the ideal location for Hitler&#x2019;s mass extermination plan. Firstly, it was situated at the center of all German-occupied countries, and secondly, its good connection to train lines made it easy to transport the detainees.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Discover nearby:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/poland\/krakow\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Krakow, Poland &#x2013; Things to do<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105715\/auschwitz-birkenau-museum.jpg\" alt=\"auschwitz birkenau museum\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"auschwitz birkenau museum\" data-id=\"46775\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105715\/auschwitz-birkenau-museum.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=46775\" class=\"wp-image-46775 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105715\/auschwitz-birkenau-museum.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105715\/auschwitz-birkenau-museum-300x4