ers were shaved and their hair was then used to produce textiles.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Discover more in our:<\/strong>&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/poland\/poland-travel-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">2-week travel guide through Poland<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105741\/auschwitz-belongings.jpg\" alt=\"auschwitz museum\"><\/noscript><img width=\"433\" height=\"338\" alt=\"auschwitz museum\" class=\"wp-image-46765 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105741\/auschwitz-belongings.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105741\/auschwitz-belongings-300x234.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105741\/auschwitz-belongings-600x469.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105741\/auschwitz-belongings-768x600.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105741\/auschwitz-belongings-1037x810.jpg 1037w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105741\/auschwitz-belongings-433x338.jpg 433w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105741\/auschwitz-belongings-1536x1200.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.sa