v>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105755\/Concentration-Camp-tour.jpg\" alt=\"Concentration Camp tour\"><\/noscript><img width=\"427\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Concentration Camp tour\" class=\"wp-image-46758 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105755\/Concentration-Camp-tour.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105755\/Concentration-Camp-tour-300x238.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105755\/Concentration-Camp-tour-600x475.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105755\/Concentration-Camp-tour-758x600.jpg 758w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105755\/Concentration-Camp-tour-1023x810.jpg 1023w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105755\/Concentration-Camp-tour-427x338.jpg 427w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105755\/Concentration-Camp-tour-1536x1216.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105755\/Concentration-Camp-tour-30x24.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105755\/Concentration-Camp-tour-163x129.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105755\/Concentration-Camp-tour-227x180.jpg 227w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105755\/Concentration-Camp-tour-768x608.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105755\/Concentration-Camp-tour-1024x811.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105755\/Concentration-Camp-tour-1364x1080.jpg 1364w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105755\/Concentration-Camp-tour-1819x1440.jpg 1819w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105755\/Concentration-Camp-tour-30x24.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105755\/Concentration-Camp-tour.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-2-complete-tour-including-transport-from-krakow\">2 &#x2013; Complete tour including transport from Krakow<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>You will likely be staying in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/poland\/krakow\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Krakow<\/a> during your visit to Auschwitz. A complete organized tour, including transport from Krakow (1.5h one-way), is the easiest option. Prices for these tours start at 30 EUR.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-3-self-guided-free-tour\">3 &#x2013; Self guided free tour<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>If you&#x2019;re on a tight budget, you will be able to purchase a free ticket on the Auschwitz website without a guide. However, be aware that these tickets are only for timeslots in the afternoon.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-are-pictures-allowed-at-auschwitz\">Are pictures allowed at Auschwitz?<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Yes, you are allowed to take pictures. Just remember to disable your flash, as this might harm the items displayed.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-how-long-is-the-tour-at-auschwitz\">How long is the tour at Auschwitz?<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The tour at Auschwitz-Birkenau is 3.5 hours. However, if you&#x2019;re coming from Krakow, you should add another 3 hours for transportation.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105738\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-everything-you-need-to-know-810x810.jpg\" alt=\"auschwitz concentration camp everything you need to know\"><\/noscript><img width=\"338\" height=\"338\" alt=\"auschwitz concentration camp everything you need to know\" class=\"wp-image-46766 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105738\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-everything-you-need-to-know-810x810.jpg 810w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105738\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-everything-you-need-to-know-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105738\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-everything-you-need-to-know-100x100.jpg 100w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105738\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-everything-you-need-to-know-600x600.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105738\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-everything-you-need-to-know-338x338.jpg 338w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105738\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-everything-you-need-to-know-1536x1536.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105738\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-everything-you-need-to-know-30x30.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105738\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-everything-you-need-to-know-163x163.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105738\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-everything-you-need-to-know-180x180.jpg 180w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105738\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-everything-you-need-to-know-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105738\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-everything-you-need-to-know-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105738\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-everything-you-need-to-know-1080x1080.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105738\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-everything-you-need-to-know-1440x1440.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105738\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-everything-you-need-to-know.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105738\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-everything-you-need-to-know-30x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/23105738\/auschwitz-concentration-camp-everything-you-need-to-know-810x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"transport\">How to get at Auschwitz-Birkenau<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Auschwitz-Birkenau Memorial and Museum is around 1.5-hour from Krakow. There are a few options for getting there.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-by-organized-tour\">By organized tour<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The easiest option is obviously by organized tour. The tour generally takes 7 hours, including 3 hours of driving. Book your tour <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/auschwitz-tickets\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">easily online here.<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-by-public-transport\">By public transport<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The train from Krakow Glowny station to Oswiecim takes around 2 hours and 20 min and costs 16 ZL (3.5 EUR). Oswiecim&#x2019;s station is about 2 KM from Auschwitz; you can get on a local bus or walk.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Alternatively, take the train from Krakow to Krzeszowice and switch to the bus towards Oswiecim. This journey should take 2 hours in total.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"What was Auschwitz? What happened at Auschwitz? Tour at Auschwitz-Birkenau Entrance Tickets How to get there What was Auschwitz?&#xA0; Originally, Auschwitz was conceived as a detention center for Polish anti-Nazi activists, politicians, etc. who were arrested when Germany took control over the country in 1939.&#xA0;&#xA0; The Nazis were a mass movement in Germany, led by [&hellip;]","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":46766,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_relevanssi_hide_post":"","_relevanssi_pin_for_all":"","_relevanssi_pin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_unpin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_include_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_exclude_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_no_append":"","_relevanssi_related_not_related":"","_relevanssi_related_posts":"918,4721,4960,4232,7212,7094"},"categories":[4750,7167,9],"tags":[78,54],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v19.3 (Yoast SEO v19.7.1) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>How to visit Auschwitz Concentration Camp in